ingredientsDesc:
AxSYM  Anti-Tg Reagent Pack
1 Bottle (9.7mL) purified thyroglobulin (human thyroid tissue extract) coated microparticles in TRIS buffer with protein (bovine) stabilizer. 
1 Bottle (9.8mL) Anti-Human IgG (goat): Alkaline Phosphatase Conjugate in TRIS buffer with protein (bovine) stabilizers.
1 Bottle (28.7mL) Assay Diluent in TRIS buffer with protein (bovine) stabilizers.
1 Bottle (35.5mL) Specimen Dilution Buffer in Phosphate buffer.
AxSYM Anti-Tg Standard Calibrators
6 Bottles (4.0mL each) at conc. of 0.0, 25.0, 125.0, 250.0, 500.0 and 1000.0 IU/mL, 
AxSYM Anti-Tg Controls
2 Bottles (7.0mL each) at conc. of 0.0 and 150.0 UL/mL.
